HEADWORD: Sunburn
<hw>Sun"burn`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. &
p. p.</pos> <conjf>Sunburned</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr> or
