==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Sunburn
<hw>Sun"burn`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The burning or discoloration
produced on the skin by the heat of the sun; tan.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sun-burner</ent>⟦br⟧
